Package de.oth.blocklib.threading

Class CompletingCallable<V>

java.lang.Object
de.oth.blocklib.threading.CompletingCallable<V>
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<CompletingCallable>, java.util.concurrent.Callable<V>
class CompletingCallable<V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.concurrent.Callable<V>, java.lang.Comparable<CompletingCallable>
A wrapping callable that completes a given CompletableFuture upon completion of the Callable.call() of the inner callable. Implements the Comparable interface, so it can be used in a priority queue. If the priorities are the same a sequence number guarantees comparability in a FIFO fashion.
Author:
Loher Florian
